This is the Debian GNU/Linux prepackaged version of the netCDF Operators
(NCO).

This package was originally put together by Brian Mays <brian@debian.org>
from software obtained from
 ftp://ftp.cgd.ucar.edu/pub/zender/nco/
Beginning March, 2003, Charlie Zender attempted to merge Debian changes
into upstream source in SourceForge CVS repository
More information can be found at:
 http://nco.sourceforge.net
Modifications of NCO package for Debian GNU/Linux Copyright (C)
1999-2002 Brian Mays and are released under the GPL (on Debian systems
see "/usr/share/common-licenses/GPL").

Changes:
 * added Debian GNU/Linux package maintenance system files
 * removed makefile dependence on rpm
 * added arm support
 * added man pages

